{"type": "article", "id": 25496, "title": "树根边桌", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-15T07:10:26Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 21, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607185032KhHmj2bInMwYBqpz.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">最近有不少小边桌都从植物中获得灵感，这个橡木做的小边桌灵感源于树根。四根桌腿呈十字交叉，但它们的高度是错开的，模拟了扭曲的树根的形状，简单但很形象。从不同角度看起来都有些细微的变化，让人觉得有趣。售价 239 欧元，<a href=\"http://www.odesi.nl/roots-massief-eiken-bijzettafel\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071850307PeXG0D3kpLMlAIg.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.6875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185031GCux2dq6cs7jYO0T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185031Jcg7WpPeD6Ih1G8s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185032MdmBu8Ot5aPZShHb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}